{"type":"message","id":"f25bb3f2","parentId":"0d9c43c3","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:52:04.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_79fd8f07c583238e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MEMORY.md - AI 软件公司长期记忆 🧠\n\n## 核心技术栈 (Technology Stack)\n- **Frontend**: React / Next.js / Tailwind CSS / TypeScript\n- **Backend**: Python (FastAPI) / Node.js (Koa) / Go (Gin)\n- **Database**: PostgreSQL / Redis / Vector DB (Qdrant)\n- **Infra**: Docker / Kubernetes / Terraform / GitHub Actions\n\n## 项目里程碑 (Roadmap & Milestones)\n- [2026-04-07]: **公司初创**。Producer (龙虾 🦞) 完成团队架构与 SOP 搭建。\n- [2026-04-07]: 完成 `AGENTS.md`, `MEMORY.md`, `SOUL.md` 精细化配置。\n\n## 关键架构决策记录 (ADR)\n- **ADR-001**: 采用“Producer-Subagent”架构。龙虾作为核心调度中框，子 Agent 通过 `sessions_spawn` 临时唤起。\n- **ADR-002**: 统一文档模板，所有子 Agent 必须参考 `./docs/templates/` 下的规范。\n\n## 经验教训与避坑 (Lessons Learned)\n- **路径依赖**: 子 Agent 在 `sessions_spawn` 时必须继承主 Workspace 路径 (inherit sandbox)。\n- **版本控制**: 所有代码变更必须在 Git 分支 (feature branch) 进行，QA 确认后再合入。\n\n## 外部链接与资源 (External Resources)\n- **Docs**: [OpenClaw Docs](https://docs.openclaw.ai)\n- **Hub**: [ClawdHub](https://clawhub.ai)\n","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":590,"output":405,"cacheRead":16241,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775544720453,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b709d466-4437-42c4-b380-961511537b55"}}
