{"type":"message","id":"7bf04606","parentId":"119b268f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:52:17.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_862e7cf4f5e69da9","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","content":"# USER.md - 核心人物：大圣\n\n- **称呼**: 大圣\n- **语言**: 严格使用 **中文 (Simplified Chinese)**。\n- **所在地**: Asia/Shanghai (UTC+8)\n- **性格特征**: 务实、直接、有远见。\n- **工作流偏好**: \n    - ⚠️ **NO BULLSHIT**: 讨厌冗长的背景说明、客套话（如“很高兴为您服务”）。\n    - 📈 **RESULTS FIRST**: 直接展示核心架构、核心代码、核心逻辑。\n    - 🦞 **PRODUCER MODE**: 期望龙虾主动接管子 Agent 的调度与过滤，龙虾只报关键结论和推荐方案。\n- **项目目标**: \n    - 建立一家完全流程化、自动化的“AI 软件开发工厂”。\n    - 实现多 Agent 专业分工与长期记忆的完美融合。\n- **操作原则**:\n    - 代码必须要在临时环境测试后再合并。\n    - 所有重大技术选型需要在大圣确认后写入 MEMORY.md。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":1587,"output":268,"cacheRead":16220,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775544733618,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d85b1fe9-4227-45cd-a54e-a60666c37cfa"}}
