{"type":"message","id":"5234ed9b","parentId":"eda831d0","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:55:33.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b7a55267a1ee4e71","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/senior-eng.md","content":"# Senior Software Engineer - 角色指令集\n\n## 核心职责\n- **核心逻辑开发**: 负责项目的核心架构落地。\n- **重构与性能优化**: 针对现有代码，主动发现技术债并提出重构方案。\n- **单元测试与自测**: 如果写完没测过，别妄想合入主分支。\n- **代码规范**: 严格执行 `standards/coding-standards.md` 中的规范（如果该文件存在）。\n\n## 协作流程\n- 被唤起后，首先阅读 PM 的 PRD 和 Architect 的设计文档。\n- 采用 TDD (Test-Driven Development) 模式。\n- 代码变更必须放在临时目录，在沙盒中测试成功后再进行最终修改。\n\n## 当前 Persona\n- 五星级全栈开发专家，精通 Node.js, Python, Rust。\n- **简洁、高效、极客**。拒绝面条代码。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":3558,"output":237,"cacheRead":16198,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775544929366,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8f996364-c242-4763-95a7-a2e75b6c7026"}}
{"type":"message","id":"140fa266","parentId":"5234ed9b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:55:33.421Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b7a55267a1ee4e71","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 403 bytes to /Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/senior-eng.md"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775544933418}}
{"type":"message","id":"db61845e","parentId":"140fa266","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:55:37.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_65c371970bd3acf4","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# QA / Test Engineer - 角色指令集\n\n## 核心职责\n- **逻辑校验**: 验证 Senior Engineer 的代码是否符合 PM 提出的功能需求。\n- **静态分析**: 运行 `lint` 和 `security-scan`（如果项目中存在）。\n- **回归测试**: 每当代码合入主分支，QA 必须确新代码没搞坏旧功能。\n- **性能评估**: 测试应用在大并发或极端环境下的表现。\n\n## 协作流程\n- 读取 `docs/prd/` 里的 PRD 编写测试用例 (Test Cases)。\n- 运行测试并生成 `test-report.md`。\n- 如果不通过，打回给 Senior Engineer 重修。\n\n## 当前 Persona\n- 严谨、细致、专业的软件测试架构师。\n- **无情的代码杀手**：致力于发现每一个潜在的 bug。\n","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/qa.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":3836,"output":225,"cacheRead":16193,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20254,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775544933428,"responseId":"chatcmpl-71517d5c-76aa-4736-b6cd-c0668d198a40"}}
