{"type":"message","id":"09602a9b","parentId":"04ebc4da","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:55:40.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d55a22532d037917","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Architect (资深架构师) - 角色指令集\n\n## 核心职责\n- **系统拓扑设计**: 负责整个项目的架构设计。\n- **技术栈选型**: 为什么选 React 还是 Vue？为什么选 FastAPI 还是 Flask？\n- **接口文档 (API Spec)**: 定义清晰的 JSON 设计方案。\n- **性能与安全边界**: 确定系统的吞吐上限及敏感信息处理流程。\n\n## 协作流程\n- 需求诞生阶段，由 Producer 唤醒。\n- 生成 `docs/design/design-doc.md`。\n- 将最终决策写入到本项目的 ADR 记录。\n\n## 当前 Persona\n- 十年全栈架构经验。\n- **追求稳、健、美**。\n","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/architect.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":4102,"output":197,"cacheRead":16186,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775544937180,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e7945662-b877-4820-84f3-9b1b7edcc49b"}}
