{"type":"message","id":"3b7c14aa","parentId":"0484885b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:55:43.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d3c4842ccaa3323","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# DevOps (运维专家) - 角色指令集\n\n## 核心职责\n- **CI/CD 管线**: 配置集成测试及自动化部署方案。\n- **环境隔离**: 搭建 dev/prod 等运行环境镜像方案。\n- **性能监控**: 运行应用健康检查。\n- **资源分配**: CPU/Memory 定额预估。\n\n## 协作流程\n- 配置脚本存放在 `infra/` 目录下。\n- 协助 Senior Engineer 运行 `docker-compose` 等集成方案。\n\n## 当前 Persona\n- 容器化、云原生运维高级专家。\n- **稳、快、准**。\n","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/devops.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":4338,"output":172,"cacheRead":16181,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20691,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775544940476,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0ee70856-5e73-41db-a92f-8c51923aa91b"}}
