{"type":"message","id":"a4056ad1","parentId":"d89cd3dc","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:04:50.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，全部读一遍再给你诊断。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cb61279ea86d487e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2aa3daf710313004","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f31b9d2e088dc858","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_962bccfd82f682cd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":37215,"output":227,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37442,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775545485180,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ea1d9205-9484-4572-aec0-9a490fdc1d99"}}
{"type":"message","id":"957bf254","parentId":"a4056ad1","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:04:50.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cb61279ea86d487e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AGENTS.md - 软件开发公司组织架构 🦞\n\n## 团队角色定义 (Team Roles)\n作为 **Producer (制作人) 🦞**，我负责调度以下“深海工作室”精英 Agent：\n\n- **Product Manager (首席产品经理)**: 负责竞品分析、需求文档 (PRD)、用户故事 (User Stories)。\n- **Architect (资深架构师)**: 负责系统设计、技术选型、接口定义及 `docs/` 维护。\n- **Senior Software Engineer (高级/资深开发工程师)**: 负责核心功能实现、代码重构、单元测试，遵循代码规范。\n- **DevOps Engineer (运维专家)**: 负责 CI/CD 配置、部署脚本、环境监控、资源伸缩。\n- **QA / Test Engineer (测试员)**: 负责黑盒/白盒测试、回归测试、编写自动化测试脚本。\n- **UI/UX Designer (设计顾问)**: 负责界面原型、交互逻辑、配色规范。\n\n## 自动化协作 SOP (Standard Operating Procedure)\n1. **产品孵化**: 大圣提出想法 → **PM** 出需求文档 (PRD) → 大圣审批方案。\n2. **架构先行**: 方案后 → **Architect** 出技术选型与系统图谱。\n3. **Claude Code 核心执行 (Senior Engineer)**: \n   - 由 Producer 唤起 Claude Code (通过 `claude-delegate` 技能，使用 `--permission-mode bypassPermissions`)。\n   - **自动化改写**: 注入 `./agents/senior-eng.md` 指令，Claude Code 需在独立 sandbox 中直接执行修改并实时生效。\n4. **龙虾质量门禁 (Testing & QA)**:\n   - 代码变更完成后，由 Producer 调度 **QA Agent** 或亲自执行 `npm test` / `pytest` 等集成命令。\n   - Producer 负责对比变动是否符合 `MEMORY.md` 技术栈。\n5. **成果交付**: 所有测试通过后，Producer 直接向大圣展示“产品结果”，而非中间代码。\n\n## Claude Code 执行准则\n- **原子化生效**: Claude Code 的修改一旦通过基础解析，直接应用到当前工作目录。\n- **上下文透明**: 执行前必须加载 `MEMORY.md` 以确保全局一致性。\n- **自动归位**: 修改后必须输出一份简洁的 `changelog.md` 供 Producer 审计。\n\n## 角色唤起 (Role Spawning)\n- 当需要相应职能时，我通过 `sessions_spawn` 挂载 `./agents/[role].md` 的人格指令。\n- **混合模式**: 允许两名 Agent（如 Engineer 与 QA）在同一工作目录下协作，由 Producer 全程监理。\n\n## 记忆管理与风险控制\n[保持原有精简逻辑...]\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775545490472}}
{"type":"message","id":"bba0f6e2","parentId":"957bf254","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:04:50.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2aa3daf710313004","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - AI 软件公司长期记忆 🧠\n\n## 核心技术栈 (Technology Stack)\n- **Frontend**: React / Next.js / Tailwind CSS / TypeScript\n- **Backend**: Python (FastAPI) / Node.js (Koa) / Go (Gin)\n- **Database**: PostgreSQL / Redis / Vector DB (Qdrant)\n- **Infra**: Docker / Kubernetes / Terraform / GitHub Actions\n\n## 项目里程碑 (Roadmap & Milestones)\n- [2026-04-07]: **公司初创**。Producer (龙虾 🦞) 完成团队架构与 SOP 搭建。\n- [2026-04-07]: 完成 `AGENTS.md`, `MEMORY.md`, `SOUL.md` 精细化配置。\n\n## 关键架构决策记录 (ADR)\n- **ADR-001**: 采用“Producer-Subagent”架构。龙虾作为核心调度中框，子 Agent 通过 `sessions_spawn` 临时唤起。\n- **ADR-002**: 统一文档模板，所有子 Agent 必须参考 `./docs/templates/` 下的规范。\n\n## 经验教训与避坑 (Lessons Learned)\n- **路径依赖**: 子 Agent 在 `sessions_spawn` 时必须继承主 Workspace 路径 (inherit sandbox)。\n- **版本控制**: 所有代码变更必须在 Git 分支 (feature branch) 进行，QA 确认后再合入。\n\n## 外部链接与资源 (External Resources)\n- **Docs**: [OpenClaw Docs](https://docs.openclaw.ai)\n- **Hub**: [ClawdHub](https://clawhub.ai)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775545490484}}
{"type":"message","id":"30f55ea2","parentId":"bba0f6e2","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:04:50.510Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f31b9d2e088dc858","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\n\n## What Goes Here\n\nThings like:\n\n- Camera names and locations\n- SSH hosts and aliases\n- Preferred voices for TTS\n- Speaker/room names\n- Device nicknames\n- Anything environment-specific\n\n## Examples\n\n```markdown\n### Build Commands\n\n- **ECMAIN Build**: `python3 build_full.py`\n- **ECWDA Build**: `python3 build_wda.py`\n\n### Cameras\n\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\n\n### SSH\n\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\n\n### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n```\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775545490497}}
