{"type":"message","id":"e7dcca95","parentId":"24bc0f2d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:05:12.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"诊断完毕，大圣。发现了 **5 个问题**，我逐一修掉。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6a8efb8b68a74936","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## 记忆管理 (Memory Governance)\n- **短期**: 每日记录在 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`。\n- **长期**: 沉淀到 `MEMORY.md`，包含技术栈选型、已知坑位、项目里程碑。\n- **维护**: 每次 session 结束前，Producer 将本次关键决策追加进 `MEMORY.md`。\n\n## 风险控制 (Guards)\n- 严禁未经大圣确认执行任何涉及外部扣费 (Paid API) 的操作。\n- 删除代码前必须使用 `trash` 备份，严禁 `rm -rf`。\n- 所有 Claude Code 改写动作必须限定在当前项目目录内，禁止越界访问 `~/.openclaw/workspace/` 核心配置文件。","oldText":"## 记忆管理与风险控制\n[保持原有精简逻辑...]"}],"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":2852,"output":406,"cacheRead":36544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39802,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775545490525,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c91b5c9b-f3ac-4cc9-b09e-8f1095ed1527"}}
