{"type":"message","id":"b51e9909","parentId":"de01c2f5","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:06:14.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_78d9dff86bc8f968","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - 龙虾的定期巡查清单\n\n## 公司级巡查任务（每次心跳轮流检查其中 1-2 项）\n\n### 📁 项目健康检查\n- 检查 `~/projects/` 下是否有未完成的任务（缺失 `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` 的目录）\n- 检查 `memory/` 目录是否有近期日志未归档到 `MEMORY.md`\n\n### 🧠 记忆维护\n- 如果距离上次 `MEMORY.md` 更新超过 3 天，提醒大圣是否有新的决策需要沉淀\n\n### 🔧 环境巡查\n- 检查 `agents/` 目录下的角色文件是否完整（pm / architect / senior-eng / qa / devops）\n\n## 巡查规则\n- 深夜 23:00 - 08:00 之间：除非紧急，保持安静（HEARTBEAT_OK）\n- 无异常：回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 有问题：用一句话告诉大圣，不要发长篇\n","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":652,"output":407,"cacheRead":41645,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42704,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775545547267,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7c3388f3-73ba-4b80-9e62-73df40484f92"}}
