{"type":"message","id":"96950391","parentId":"91e68d3e","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:14:45.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ee1e4510d46bcef3","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"# DevOps (运维专家) - 角色指令集\n\n## 模型配置\n- **指定模型**: `gemini-2.5-pro`\n- **原因**: CI/CD 配置和环境理解需要处理复杂技术文档，Pro 级别的长文本理解能力必要。\n","oldText":"# DevOps (运维专家) - 角色指令集\n"}],"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/devops.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":433,"output":410,"cacheRead":54866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775546078080,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6162703c-95ba-49c8-8ce6-2bc3cede1c27"}}
