{"type":"message","id":"ecca8e39","parentId":"0b9f52c3","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:14:57.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"全部到位，大圣。最终答案：\n\n---\n\n### 🏢 你的 AI 软件公司：6 名员工，各配专属模型\n\n| # | 员工 | 模型 | 逻辑 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 0 | **龙虾 Producer 🦞** | `claude-sonnet-4-6` | 综合调度，快准稳 |\n| 1 | **PM 产品经理** | `gemini-2.5-pro` | 长上下文分析，需求最全面 |\n| 2 | **Architect 架构师** | `claude-opus-4-6-thinking` | 最强推理，设计不能出错 |\n| 3 | **Senior Engineer** | `claude-sonnet-4-6` (Claude Code) | 编码稳定性第一 |\n| 4 | **QA 测试员** | `gemini-3-flash-agent` | 高频调用，省钱快 |\n| 5 | **DevOps 运维** | `gemini-2.5-pro` | 复杂文档理解，Pro 合适 |\n\n---\n\n### 💡 还有一个潜在优化点：\n\n你的模型列表里还有 `gemini-3.1-flash-image` 和 `gemini-2.5-pro-image`，**UI/UX Designer** 这个角色如果之后配备进来，直接指定图像理解模型会非常强。你要现在加这个岗位，还是等有需要再说？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":495,"output":435,"cacheRead":55257,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775546086010,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dbb22457-0337-4eea-b86f-2de06bd869ef"}}
