{"type":"message","id":"91909064","parentId":"a7b3e965","timestamp":"2026-04-07T08:31:11.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定，大圣。\n\n### ✅ 本次修改：\n1. **PM + DevOps** 模型 → `gemini-3.1-pro-high`（三处同步：角色文件 + AGENTS.md 总表）\n2. **MEMORY.md 优化**：\n   - 补全里程碑记录（含模型修正、角色库建立等事件）\n   - 新增 ADR-004（模型分级配置策略）\n   - 新增避坑经验：模型 ID 必须与 `openclaw.json` 对齐\n   - 修正错别字（\"中框\"→\"中枢\"、\"权\"→\"由\"）\n\n所有文件已就绪，没有悬空引用。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"claude-opus-4-6-thinking","usage":{"input":1273,"output":213,"cacheRead":80765,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775550663223,"responseId":"chatcmpl-35a70897-ab71-47be-b78d-33d8bf653e97"}}
