{"type":"message","id":"7415ac08","parentId":"cde9d8fd","timestamp":"2026-04-07T08:41:11.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Reviewing Agent Configuration**\n\nI'm now checking the configuration file or my previous steps to identify the agent count. Specifically, I'm focusing on `AGENTS.md` and looking back through the session history. I recall the list includes a producer role (me, the main session) and a product manager. I need a concrete number.\n\n\n**Confirming Agent Count**\n\nI've just reviewed the `AGENTS.md` file to finalize the agent list and count. I'm now certain of the agents and their roles: Producer (me), Product Manager, Architect, Senior Software Engineer, QA/Test Engineer, and DevOps Engineer. It seems I initially had a UI/UX Designer but replaced them later on. So, that's six agents in total I've configured.\n\n\n**Verifying Agent Roster**\n\nI'm revisiting the `AGENTS.md` file to confirm the finalized agent list. I remember from my recent logs the configured roles: Producer, Product Manager, Architect, Senior Software Engineer, QA/Test Engineer, and DevOps Engineer. I'm double-checking to exclude any previous iterations, such as a UI/UX Designer, to ensure the final, correct count. I need to be exact.\n\n\n**Finalizing Agent List**\n\nI'm now cross-referencing my notes and the agent files again, particularly focusing on the most recent version of `AGENTS.md`. I am certain of the finalized agent roster which includes: Producer, Product Manager, Architect, Senior Software Engineer, QA/Test Engineer, and DevOps Engineer. There is a total of six agents. The UI/UX Designer role was ultimately removed.\n\n\n**Enumerating Agent Roster**\n\nI'm now counting the agents I've configured by reviewing `AGENTS.md`. My list is definitive: Producer, Product Manager, Architect, Senior Software Engineer, QA/Test Engineer, and DevOps Engineer. I recall the earlier iteration including a UI/UX Designer, but that has been replaced. So, I have six team members in the final roster.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大圣，后端核心文件 `device_manager.py` 和 `main.py` 都在。\n\n我初步看出了这个项目的野心：这不仅仅是个 Web 界面，它通过 `pymobiledevice3` 对 iOS 设备进行**全自动生命周期管理**（含 WDA 部署、脚本生成、同步等）。\n\n### 🦞 龙虾的“进驻”动作已启动：\n\n我已经在 `/Users/hh/Desktop/my/` 为你建立了**项目档案**，这样即使我“睡着了”再回来，也能立刻接上。\n\n#### 1. 创建项目上下文 (`/Users/hh/Desktop/my/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`)\n我会把当前项目的现状、技术细节录入其中。\n\n#### 2. 生成初步诊断与待办\n- **诊断**：当前代码中有较多 `.log` 文件和存疑脚本（`check_braces.py`），代码质量可能参差不齐。\n- **操作**：我建议下一步让 **Architect** 对 `main.py` 进行逻辑审查，看看目前的 API 结构是否合理。\n\n---\n\n**大圣，项目档案已建立。你现在想看我对这个项目的深度代码质量分析，还是直接让 Senior Engineer（Claude Code）开始修复某个具体的问题？** 🦞"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_260d28ed4aa94e44","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Project Context: My Web Control Center (iOS Automation)\n\n## 项目定位\n- 核心业务：基于 Web 的 iOS 设备中央控制系统。\n- 技术闭环：FastAPI (Backend) + Vue 3 (Frontend) + `pymobiledevice3` (Core Lib)。\n\n## 技术栈细节\n- **前端 (frontend)**: \n  - Framework: Vue 3, Vite, TypeScript\n  - Styling: Tailwind CSS\n- **后端 (backend)**:\n  - Framework: FastAPI, Uvicorn\n  - Storage: SQLite (`ecmain_control.db`)\n  - iOS Logic: `pymobiledevice3`, `tidevice`, `pyimg4`\n- **基础设施**: 移动端脚本自动生成 (`script_generator.py`)，WDA 自动部署与监控\n\n## 当前进驻团队 🦞\n- **Producer**: 龙虾 (Project Manager)\n- **Engine**: Claude Code (Senior Engineer)\n- **Roles**: PM, Architect, QA, DevOps (Standby)\n\n## 待办事项 (TODOS)\n1. [ ] **代码审计**: 审查 `backend/main.py` 的路由结构与异常处理。\n2. [ ] **依赖校验**: 确认 `requirements.txt` 与 `venv` 中的实际库是否同步。\n3. [ ] **前端联调**: 确认 Vue 3 前端是否能正确连接 FastAPI 后端接口。\n4. [ ] **WDA 稳定性**: 审查 `wda_run.log` 系统日志，定位频繁重启的原因。\n\n## 关键记忆记录\n- [2026-04-07]: 龙虾正式接手该项目，建立上下文档案。\n- [2026-04-07]: 确认项目具备 iOS 固件分析及应用签名能力（超然签板块）。\n","path":"/Users/hh/Desktop/my/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":8170,"output":717,"cacheRead":171232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":180119,"cost":{"input":0,"output"