{"type":"message","id":"f4e04a7f","parentId":"dbd8c451","timestamp":"2026-04-07T08:41:25.092Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Recalling Team Composition**\n\nI need to quickly recall the number of agents I configured, but I need to consult the `AGENTS.md` file, or my recent notes. I recall I'm the producer agent, (龙虾 🦞) within the main session.\n\n\n**Confirming Team Members**\n\nI've got the initial list of agents: PM, Architect, Senior Engineer, QA, and DevOps, all in their respective markdown files. I'm now checking `AGENTS.md` for the final team composition, as I seem to recall a UI/UX Designer was there previously. I need to ensure this is accurate before reporting the total number.\n\n\n**Verifying Team Count**\n\nI'm double-checking the definitive team list against the `AGENTS.md` file. The user needs the precise agent count. I have the initial set: Producer, PM, Architect, Senior Engineer, QA, and DevOps, but I recall a UI/UX Designer was considered. I'm cross-referencing my recent notes and the markdown files to finalize the count. It looks like the list is the same, so there are six team members.\n\n\n**Finalizing Team List**\n\nI'm now cross-referencing my notes with the `AGENTS.md` file to confirm the final agent count for the team. My current list consists of: Producer, PM, Architect, Senior Software Engineer, QA/Test Engineer, and DevOps Engineer. I need to be sure before I report the total team size. I remember adding a UI/UX Designer previously, but I think this was removed. I must verify the team count for the user.\n\n\n**Confirming Team Membership**\n\nI'm now revisiting the agent list, ensuring no omissions. My recent review confirms the agents are the Producer (myself), PM, Architect, Senior Engineer, QA/Test Engineer, and DevOps Engineer. There were some notes about UI/UX, but I need to be 100% sure this agent is included. I will revisit the `AGENTS.md` file one last time to ensure the definitive list is correct.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"档案已建立在 `/Users/hh/Desktop/my/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`。\n\n大圣，我现在正式带队入驻。作为 Producer 🦞，我的第一份作战计划如下：\n\n1.  **代码探路**（由我执行）：我会阅读 `backend/main.py` 和 `backend/device_manager.py`，搞清楚目前 API 的核心逻辑，是否存在导致 WDA 重启的严重 Bug。\n2.  **启动 Architect**：生成一份**系统架构图**，通过 Web 界面到底是怎么控制真机的。\n3.  **启动 Senior Engineer (Claude Code)**：直接修复我发现的逻辑漏洞。\n\n**你现在是想让我展示第一步的“代码质量诊断报告”，还是有什么眼下最火急火燎的问题（比如界面进不去或者设备连不上）需要我优先处理？** 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":2445,"output":188,"cacheRead":179388,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":182021,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775551271560,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5b7d7ff0-0e07-47d3-800f-27e7d7e21f5c"}}
