{"type":"compaction","id":"c46b7b96","parentId":"798326e9","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:56:24.557Z","summary":"## Goal\nSet up a multi-agent AI software development company within OpenClaw workspace, with specialized roles, long-term memory, Claude Code integration, and properly configured models. Additionally: fully analyze, document, and familiarize all agents with the `web_control_center` project codebase.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- All communication in Simplified Chinese\n- Address user as \"大圣\"\n- Producer (龙虾 🦞) is the main orchestrator\n- Claude Code handles actual code writing (Senior Engineer role)\n- Code changes go live directly; Producer (not user) tests and reviews\n- User only sees final product results\n- Full permissions granted: file operations, network access, shell commands, sub-agent spawning\n- Hard limits: paid API calls, public deployments, irreversible deletions require user confirmation\n- No bullshit — direct results, no fluff\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md` — org chart, permissions, SOP, Claude Code rules, risk controls\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md` — tech stack, ADRs (001-004), milestones, operating rules, lessons learned\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md` — Producer persona, principles, network autonomy, max authorization\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md` — user profile, preferences, project goals\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md` — Lobster identity card\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md` — Claude Code integration, skill paths, agent template paths, build commands\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md` — periodic audit tasks for project health, memory maintenance, agent file integrity\n- [x] Created `agents/pm.md` — model: `gemini-3.1-pro-high`\n- [x] Created `agents/architect.md` — model: `claude-opus-4-6-thinking`\n- [x] Created `agents/senior-eng.md` — model: `claude-sonnet-4-6` (via Claude Code)\n- [x] Created `agents/qa.md` — model: `gemini-3-flash-agent`\n- [x] Created `agents/devops.md` — model: `gemini-3.1-pro-high`\n- [x] Updated `/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json` — fixed all `maxTokens` from 4096 to proper values (Claude Opus: 32000, Claude Sonnet: 16000, Gemini 2.5 Pro: 65536, Pro series: 32768, Flash series: 8192, image gen: 4096 kept)\n- [x] Fixed model ID mismatch: `gemini-3.1-pro` → `gemini-3.1-pro-high` in pm.md, devops.md, AGENTS.md table\n- [x] Fixed MEMORY.md structure (added missing section headers, expanded milestones, added ADR-004)\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/Desktop/my/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` — project context file for web_control_center\n- [x] Created `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-07.md` — daily memory flush with team config, project takeover notes, TODOs\n- [x] Scanned full backend file structure: 4980 total lines across 11 Python files\n- [x] Read and analyzed `backend/main.py` (2228 lines) — FastAPI app with custom HMAC-SHA256 Token auth, CORS middleware, SQLite backend\n- [x] Read and analyzed `backend/device_manager.py` (483 lines) — thread-safe PortPool, iOS device lifecycle via pymobiledevice3\n- [x] Read and analyzed `backend/database.py` (1284 lines) — WAL-mode SQLite, in-memory heartbeat cache, async flush system\n- [x] Read `frontend/src/App.vue` — single-file Vue 3 app with smart API base detection (local vs ecmain.site), full auth flow with `authFetch` wrapper and 401 interceptor\n- [x] Confirmed frontend is a **monolithic single-component app** (only App.vue + HelloWorld.vue, no router, no store)\n- [x] Confirmed `backend/static/index.html` exists — frontend is built and served statically by FastAPI\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Deep code analysis of remaining backend files: `platform_utils.py`, `proxy_parser.py`, `script_generator.py`, `sync_tk.py`\n- [ ] Full API route inventory from `main.py` (file was truncated at 37985 chars)\n- [ ] Generate comprehensive architecture documentation for all agents\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Producer-Subagent architecture**: Lobster (Producer) is the central orchestrator; sub-agents spawned via `sessions_spawn` with role-specific `.md` persona files\n- **Claude Code = Senior Engineer**: Code writing delegated to Claude Code engine with `--permission-mode bypassPermissions`; changes go live immediately\n- **Model tiering**: Architect → Opus (deep reasoning); Engineer → Sonnet (code stability); PM/DevOps → Gemini 3.1 Pro High (long context); QA → Flash (high-frequency, cost-efficient)\n- **Project vs. global config**: Each project gets a `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`; local project settings override `MEMORY.md` on conflicts\n- **Model ID alignment rule**: Agent `.md` files must use exact IDs from `openclaw.json` (learned from `gemini-3.1-pro` bug)\n- **Frontend architecture finding**: The frontend is a single monolithic `App.vue` — no Vue Router, no Pinia/Vuex; all state managed in one component. This is a major refactoring target.\n- **Dual-mode serving**: FastAPI serves built Vue frontend as static files from `backend/static/`; dev mode uses Vite dev server separately\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Complete reading remaining backend files (`platform_utils.py`, `proxy_parser.py`, `script_generator.py`, `sync_tk.py`)\n2. Extract full API route list from `main.py` (GET/POST/WebSocket endpoints)\n3. Generate **Architecture Document** (`/Users/hh/Desktop/my/ARCHITECTURE.md`) covering: system topology, data flow, API inventory, DB schema, known issues\n4. Generate **Code Quality Report** highlighting: monolithic App.vue (refactor needed), missing error handling patterns, log file clutter, token secret hardcoded fallback\n5. Restart OpenClaw Gateway to apply `openclaw.json` changes: `openclaw gateway restart`\n6. Test the full pipeline with a small real task\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Workspace**: `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/`\n- **Config file**: `/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- **Agent templates**: `/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/` (pm.md, architect.md, senior-eng.md, qa.md, devops.md)\n- **Team roster**: 6 members — Producer 🦞, PM, Architect, Senior Engineer, QA, DevOps\n- **Available model IDs** (exact, from openclaw.json): `gemini-3-flash-agent`, `gemini-2.5-flash-thinking`, `claude-sonnet-4-6`, `gemini-2.5-flash`, `gemini-2.5-pro`, `gemini-3.1-flash-lite`, `gemini-3-pro-low`, `gemini-3-flash`, `gemini-3.1-flash-image`, `gemini-3.1-pro-low`, `gemini-2.5-flash-lite`, `gpt-oss-120b-medium`, `gemini-3.1-pro-high`, `claude-opus-4-6-thinking`, `gemini-3-pro-high`, `gemini-3-pro-image`\n- **Default primary model** in openclaw.json: `custom/gemini-3-flash`\n- **Project path**: `/Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/`\n  - Backend: FastAPI + SQLite (`ecmain_control.db`) + `pymobiledevice3` — **2228-line main.py**\n  - Frontend: Vue 3 monolithic single-component app (App.vue only, no router/store)\n  - iOS libs: `pymobiledevice3==7.7.1`, `tidevice==0.12.11`, `psutil==7.2.2`\n  - Entry points: `start.py`, `start_web.sh`\n  - Auth: Custom HMAC-SHA256 token (7-day expiry); secret falls back to hardcoded string if env var missing\n  - DB: WAL-mode SQLite with in-memory heartbeat cache (`HEARTBEAT_CACHE` + `LATEST_STATUS_CACHE`) and background flush thread\n  - WDA logs: `wda_run.log`, `wda_deploy.log` — WDA restart stability is a known concern\n- **超然签 board**: `/Users/hh/Desktop/my/超然签/` — contains `.ipa` files + iOS kernelcache (signing/jailbreak related)\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\n用户说\"继续\"，要求继续深度读取所有文件并生成完整的项目档案。\n\n## Early Progress\n- AI开始系统性地读取项目文件\n- 读取了 `backend/database.py`（offset=100, limit=400）：包含数据库初始化逻辑，创建了 `ec_execution_times`、`ec_exec_times` 表，自动清理3天未活跃的\"僵尸\"设备，以及通过 ALTER TABLE 动态添加多个字段（`ecwda_status`、`config_ip`、`config_vpn`、`apple_account`、`apple_password`、`tiktok_accounts`、`task_status` 等）\n- 读取了 `backend/main.py`（offset=900, limit=600）：包含 WDA（WebDriverAgent）操作相关端点，支持多种连接模式（ws/lan/auto），实现了 `WDA_WINDOW_SIZE`、`WDA_SCREENSHOT`、`ping` 等指令分支，使用 SIZE_CACHE 缓存窗口尺寸\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- 项目是一个 Web 控制中心（`web_control_center`），包含 backend（FastAPI/Python）和前端\n- 后端核心文件为 `database.py` 和 `main.py`，已读取部分内容\n- AI正在继续读取更多文件内容以生成完整项目档案\n- 两个文件都有大量截断内容（13159 和 27712 个字符被截断），说明文件内容非常庞大，仍有大量未读取的内容\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-07-agent-team.md\n/Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/backend/database.py\n/Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/backend/main.py\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/architect.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/devops.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/pm.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/qa.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/senior-eng.md\n/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-07.md\n/Users/hh/Desktop/my/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"98be8fed","tokensBefore":91205,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-07-agent-team.md","/Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/backend/database.py","/Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/backend/main.py"],"modifiedFiles":["/Users/hh/.openclaw/openclaw.json","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/architect.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/devops.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/pm.md","/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/qa.