{"type":"message","id":"70190048","parentId":"50cebcef","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:16:23.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 啊！明白了，大圣！\n\n你说的是 ECMAIN 在心跳里上报的 `device_no`（其实我们代码里通常用 `identifierForVendor` 作为心跳的唯一主键被存为了 `udid` 字段，而真机的硬件 UDID 在 USB 层是另一套）。\n\n无论是心跳还是主动查询版本，核心矛盾是：**主动发起检查版本的接口如果没带可以识别身份的 ID，后端就没法查它到底有没有在跑任务。**\n\n让我们先看看客户端是怎么发这个 GET 请求的。如果它是 ECMAIN App 主动发起的，我们需要让 ECMAIN 在请求 `/api/ecmain/version` 时带上它自己的唯一识别码。\n\n我先看看现在 `main.py` 里的 `api_ecmain_version` 接口修改怎么做："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1f5638842dcb0c40","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"def api_ecmain_version\" -A 10 /Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/backend/main.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":3124,"output":229,"cacheRead":48805,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52158,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775556975206,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2c5c5526-86aa-4ce9-b8d4-4228dba6b6cf"}}
