{"type":"message","id":"7f8744af","parentId":"feeae287","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:17:03.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"大圣，如果你能接触到 ECMAIN 的 iOS 工程源码（Objective-C），记得提醒负责 iOS 的同学：\n\n**在 ECMAIN 主动请求升级的接口调用中，需要带上自身的 `udid` 字段（即 `device_no` 或 `identifierForVendor`，和心跳中上报的值保持一致）：**\n```text\n原来: GET /api/ecmain/version\n修改后: GET /api/ecmain/version?udid=<你心跳里用的唯一码>\n```\n\n只要它带上了，服务器就能拦截住。\n\n我确认一下前端页面有没有用到这俩接口，如果有的话也要更新。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7afedab5bcf158c4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"/api/ecmain/version\\|/api/ecwda/version\" /Users/hh/Desktop/my/web_control_center/frontend/src/App.vue"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":54427,"output":197,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54624,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775557013360,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bd778da1-a04d-4a1e-8903-3ea6894a1121"}}
