{"type":"message","id":"59598fce","parentId":"9152e5de","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:28:29.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So the App ID is indeed `cli_a95e7a8914ba5cc2`.\n\nOkay, there is another very likely problem. The Feishu domain could be `feishu.cn` or `larksuite.com`. The user config says: `\"domain\": \"feishu\"`.\nWait... Is there a chance the user created the App in Lark (larksuite.com) but the domain is set to Feishu?\nBut the error came from `open.feishu.cn`.\n\nWhat else could trigger \"receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app\"?\nPerhaps the app has not been \"Issued/Published\" (版本管理与发布)? If an app has never been published, its \"live\" state doesn't have the WebSocket capability enabled on Feishu's backend. This is the most common pitfall.\n\nAlso, looking at the image:\nUnder `已添加事件`:\n`机器人进群 v2.0` (im.chat.member.bot.added_v1)\nThere is **NO `接收消息` (im.message.receive_v1)** event! So even if the connection succeeds, the bot won't receive normal chat messages!\n\nI need to bluntly tell the user two things:\n1. They *still* haven't added the \"接收消息\" event. They only added \"机器人进群\". So if it connects, I won't hear them anyway.\n2. The reason for the 400 error is most likely because **they haven't clicked \"版本管理与发布\" -> \"创建版本\" -> \"申请发布\"** to actually put these settings online.\n\nLet's do a sanity check on the error message again. If it says \"only available in self-build & Feishu app\", is it possible that they selected \"商店应用\" (Store App) originally? In Feishu, if you go to \"https://open.feishu.cn/app\", you click \"创建企业自建应用\". If you click \"创建商店应用\", the sidebar is actually very similar. Wait, does the sidebar of a Store App have \"应用发布 -> 版本管理与发布\"? Yes, it might.\nHowever, if they created a Store App, they CANNOT use long connections. They MUST recreate the app as a \"企业自建应用\" (Self-built App). I should mention this explicitly.\n\nWait! The image shows: \"使用 长连接 接收事件  推 荐\". If this was a Store App, Feishu might simply hide or disable the \"长连接\" option! The very fact that the Feishu UI says \"使用 长连接 接收事件\" and they could select it, PROVES that it is a Self-built app, OR that Feishu's UI let them select it but the API rejects it later. But normally, Feishu's UI is robust. It's a self-built app.\n\nSo why the backend error \"receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app\"?\nAh! Is the app configured with some invalid payload?\nCould it be that the app HAS NOT BEEN PUBLISHED? Yes. In Feishu, if you change from Webhook to Long Connection, it *only* takes effect after you create a new version and publish. Before publishing, the Feishu backend API still thinks you are using the old method or the default method (Webhook), and any attempt to establish a persistent connection is rejected with exactly this 400 error. The error message may be a generic fallback when the backend's routing table hasn't updated to recognize this app as a WS-enabled self-built app.\n\nLet's write a very decisive response. I will use the image they provided.\n\n1. Point out the missing event.\n\"大圣，我看到你发的截图了。从截图上我已经发现了两个致命问题！\"\n\"第一：**你没有添加『接收消息』事件！** 仔细看你的截图，【已添加事件】列表里只有孤零零的一个『机器人进群』。你必须再点击右侧的蓝色按钮【添加事件】，把 `接收消息 (im.message.receive_v1)` 加进去，否则我依然收不到你说的任何一句话！\"\n\n2. Address the connection error mapping to the \"Not Published\" state.\n\"第二：既然你的界面能勾选【长连接】，说明这就是自建应用。那为什么飞书服务器依旧死活不让我连（报错只允许自建应用连接）？原因是你在后台点的这些配置，**当前全是草稿状态，根本没有同步到飞书服务器！**\"\n\"飞书的死规定：但凡在这几个页面动了任何一个配置，必须进入左侧栏的【版本管理与发布】，点击右上角【创建版本】，写个版本号，然后点【申请发布】。管理员审核通过（如果你是创建者会自动通过）后，这个配置才算真正上线！\"\n\nBecause the user is the administrator (\"大圣\"), it should auto-pass.\n\nLet me double check what `/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping` is. Is that an OpenClaw internal webhook? No, `bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping` looks like something specific. Wait, wait! Could it be that OpenClaw's Feishu plugin tries to make a test webhook call to itself? I don't need to overthink it - the log is clear enough. The connection falls back or fails, and WebSocket is rejecting.\n\nLet's just give the user the straightforward, actionable checklist based on the visual evidence.\nThis is the role of Lobster 🦞! Bold, direct, and pragmatic.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_62677d5e3995c05f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"ok\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":2995,"output":1246,"cacheRead":64989,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69230,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775561291493,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f6e3f0bb-0a6e-41a8-ad1e-7ddf27d7267e"}}
