{"type":"message","id":"6fadcbab","parentId":"bc71f652","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:29:43.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Analyzing the Feishu Troubleshooting Issue**\n\nThe user has added all necessary events (including `im.message.receive_v1`) to their Feishu Custom App (as verified by the screenshot).\nHowever, the plugin is still throwing a `400 Bad Request` at `POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping`.\n\nWait... is there an API called `/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping` in Feishu? No!\nWait. Let's look closer. Where does `bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping` come from?\nWait!! No, there's no official Feishu endpoint with `openclaw_bot` in it.\nWait, if there's no such endpoint, maybe it IS a built-in thing from some internal routing? But the error message specifically says:\n`receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app, Configured in: ...`\n\nWait, if the user added the events but did not **PUBLISH** the app (create a version and approve/publish), the Feishu backend *will still use the old configuration*. Did the user do the Version Release step as I requested? I said \"Wait, you must go to 版本管理与发布 and make a new version/publish.\" The user replied \"都加上了\" (Added them all). But did they publish?\n\nLet me look at the `AppId`.\nIs it possible the App ID `cli_a95e7a8914ba5cc2` was created under a *different* Feishu tenant than what the user is trying to connect it to? Not fully relevant to the websocket initialization error.\n\nLet me think if there's a problem with OpenClaw Gateway.\nLet me restart the gateway and check logs immediately.\n_Actually, I don't need to guess if they published, I can just ask forcefully. But wait, what if they DID publish but it still fails?_\n\nWait, I should test restarting the gateway once more to see if the fresh credentials pick up their new published version.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c38fe2575bb5e541","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart && sleep 4 && tail -n 50 ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log | grep -i \"feishu\" -C 3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":2428,"output":514,"cacheRead":69050,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71992,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775561371759,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2b8f60d8-9438-4f2b-b56d-bd535f914640"}}
