{"type":"message","id":"0f9862ab","parentId":"535df346","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:29:43.120Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Feishu log continues to show failures with `POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping`. This is the same error as before.\n\nWait exactly... Why is it pinging `openclaw_bot` endpoint?\nAh!!! I just noticed something. `https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping` is NOT a Feishu endpoint. No wait, is it? Wait! `/open-apis/bot/v1/XXX` -> is it `open-apis/bot/v1/info`? No, maybe the plugin sets its own webhook endpoint inside Feishu!\n\nLet me read the logs carefully right after a restart.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_16ca5d217dc41416","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart && sleep 5 && tail -n 100 ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log | grep -i \"feishu\" -C 5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":1948,"output":215,"cacheRead":69006,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71169,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775564974966,"responseId":"chatcmpl-96148a67-3b57-4b21-a339-375148318293"}}
