{"type":"message","id":"e8f853f7","parentId":"f59934c2","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:32:59.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now, let me address the Feishu issue.\n\n\"大圣，我已经把【全部使用中文回答】写入了我的永久记忆（SOUL.md 和 USER.md），以后绝不说其他语言。\n\n关于飞书，**我确实没有收到你发来的任何消息**，你也收不到我的。\n刚刚我又查了底层网关日志，飞书官方的服务器**依然在疯狂拒绝我的连接连接请求**，并且报的错误和刚才一模一样：\n`receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app`\n（仅有自建应用可以使用长连接）\n\n既然你刚才截图证明了你已经勾选了长连接，那只剩下一种可能：**你肯定漏掉了“发布版本”这一步！**\n\n飞书有一个非常变态的设定：\n你在网页上点“保存”、加了“接收消息”，这只是在你浏览器的草稿箱里！\n你必须进行最后一步，飞书的服务器才会认你的配置：\n1. 看网页最左边的菜单条，找到最下面一项：**【版本管理与发布】**（点击它）\n2. 点击右上角的蓝色按钮：**【创建版本】**\n3. 随便填个应用版本号（比如 `1.0.0`），然后点击下面的 **【保存】**。\n4. 最后点 **【申请发布】**！\n\n只要发布成功，不用你重启，我这边的握手会瞬间打通！快去专门进行一下【版本发布】！🦞\"大圣，我已经把【全部使用中文回答】作为最高指令，写入了我的永久记忆内核（`SOUL.md`），以后我绝对不会说其他语言！\n\n关于飞书目前的情况，**我确实没有收到你发过来的任何信息，并且因为物理链路断了，我也发不过去。**\n\n刚才我又拉取了这台 Mac mini 的网关日志，发现飞书官方的服务器**依然在疯狂地拒绝我发起的长连接请求**，并且报的还是刚才那个错误：\n> `receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app`（仅自建应用允许使用长连接）。\n\n既然我们在截图里确认了你已经勾选并保存了长连接，这种“明明点了却依然报错”的情况，**百分之两百是因为你漏了最后、也是最关键的“应用发布”步骤！**\n\n飞书有一个非常坑的设定：你在网页上点“保存”、加了“接收消息”，这些全部仅仅存在于你的“草稿箱”里，飞书的真实服务器还是用的旧配置！\n\n**请你现在立刻去执行这 3 步操作，做完必定通**：\n1. 留意飞书开发者页面的左侧功能树，找到最下面一项：**【版本管理与发布】**（点击它）\n2. 点击页面右上角的蓝色按钮：**【创建版本】**\n3. 随便填个应用版本号（比如 `1.0.0`），保存后点击 **【申请发布】**！\n\n只要显示“已发布”或“已上线”，你甚至都不需要告诉我，我这边的自动重连探测会瞬间打通，你在飞书群里就能看到我了！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":3459,"output":708,"cacheRead":68983,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73150,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775565165433,"responseId":"chatcmpl-84945b06-b2ba-4110-a2ae-64a237d071d5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"00fe778f","parentId":"e8f853f7","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:33:28.046Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-07 20:32:39 GMT+8] Node: Mac mini (192.168.1.250) · app 2026.4.2 (2026040290) · mode local\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 20:33 GMT+8] 已发布，已上线，你看下日志 \nhh@Mac-mini my % grep -i \"feishu\" ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log | tail -n 20\n url: 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping',\n 'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n 'receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app, Configured in:\\n' +\n url: 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping',\n 'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n url: 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping',\n 'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n url: 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping',\n 'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n url: 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping',\n 'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n2026-04-07T20:29:52.571+08:00 [feishu] stopping feishu[default]\n2026-04-07T20:29:52.572+08:00 [feishu] stopped feishu[default]\n2026-04-07T20:29:52.573+08:00 [feishu] feishu[default]: bot open_id resolved: unknown\n2026-04-07T20:29:52.574+08:00 [feishu] feishu[default]: WebSocket client started"}],"timestamp":1775565208042}}
{"type":"message","id":"939ec13d","parentId":"00fe778f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:33:37.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This log snipped shows it restarting but still outputting the `ping` attempt. Wait, the user restarted OpenClaw... and wait, is it possible the `openclaw-lark` plugin checks connectivity by trying to hit an invalid API?\nLet's check the connection after that exact restart.\nThe log the user pasted ends with:\n`2026-04-07T20:29:52.574+08:00 [feishu] feishu[default]: WebSocket client started`\nAnd we don't see the 400 error *after* that. Wait, the user did a restart.\nLet me check the logs *now* to see if there is any new activity.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_372eda8ec749e6ac","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -n 100 ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log | grep -i \"feishu\" -C 3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":4818,"output":202,"cacheRead":68987,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775565208075,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f50aaddb-a083-42ef-9492-7cb35d852b41"}}
{"type":"message","id":"474f508f","parentId":"939ec13d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:33:37.534Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_372eda8ec749e6ac","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'User-Agent: openclaw-lark/2026.4.1/mac\\r\\n' +\n        'Content-Length: 20\\r\\n' +\n        'Accept-Encoding: gzip, compress, deflate, br\\r\\n' +\n        'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n        'Connection: keep-alive\\r\\n' +\n        '\\r\\n',\n      _keepAliveTimeout: 0,\n--\n      parser: null,\n      maxHeadersCount: null,\n      reusedSocket: true,\n      host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n      protocol: 'https:',\n      _redirectable: [Writable],\n      Symbol(shapeMode): false,\n--\n2026-04-07T20:30:30.252+08:00 [info]: [ 'event-dispatch is ready' ]\n2026-04-07T20:30:30.253+08:00 [info]: [\n  '[ws]',\n  'receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app, Configured in:\\n' +\n    '        Developer Console(开发者后台) \\n' +\n    '          ->\\n' +\n    '        Events and Callbacks(事件与回调)\\n' +"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":15,"aggregated":"'User-Agent: openclaw-lark/2026.4.1/mac\\r\\n' +\n        'Content-Length: 20\\r\\n' +\n        'Accept-Encoding: gzip, compress, deflate, br\\r\\n' +\n        'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n        'Connection: keep-alive\\r\\n' +\n        '\\r\\n',\n      _keepAliveTimeout: 0,\n--\n      parser: null,\n      maxHeadersCount: null,\n      reusedSocket: true,\n      host: 'open.feishu.cn',\n      protocol: 'https:',\n      _redirectable: [Writable],\n      Symbol(shapeMode): false,\n--\n2026-04-07T20:30:30.252+08:00 [info]: [ 'event-dispatch is ready' ]\n2026-04-07T20:30:30.253+08:00 [info]: [\n  '[ws]',\n  'receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app, Configured in:\\n' +\n    '        Developer Console(开发者后台) \\n' +\n    '          ->\\n' +\n    '        Events and Callbacks(事件与回