{"type":"message","id":"7af4b5f1","parentId":"50c9012a","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:34:57.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OH MY GOD! `open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping` is a real API endpoint! Wait, it works! Wait, but it is returning `code: 0`!\nWhy was Axios returning 400?\nAh! Because earlier the token fetching MIGHT HAVE FAILED or something? No...\nWait, let's curl another endpoint: `https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v3/info`.\nLet's see why the OpenClaw plugin was failing a few minutes ago.\nWait, right now it is returning `{\"code\":0,\"msg\":\"\",\"data\":{\"pingBotInfo\":{\"botID\":\"ou_760c4bed06025043478956c9ac7e01e4\",\"botName\":\"openclaw\"}}}`. That means the bot is up! The connection works from curl!\n\nSo what is the state of the plugin NOW?\nLet's check `tail -n 100 ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log` again.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5b208580b79eacbf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -i \"feishu\\|websocket\" ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log | tail -n 20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":2266,"output":275,"cacheRead":77057,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775565291410,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cc7bd574-55b9-4866-a2c4-a5aab29cfd25"}}
