{"type":"message","id":"bca5b53e","parentId":"3e6a8772","timestamp":"2026-04-07T12:35:53.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wait, that is HTTP 200, not 400!\nFeishu API usually returns 200 for logical errors.\n\nThen why did `Axios` log `response: { status: 400, statusText: 'Bad Request' }` for `url: 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping'`?\nLet me replicate EXACTLY the Axios request!\nNotice what Axios sends:\n```\n      _header: 'POST /open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping HTTP/1.1\\r\\n' +\n        'Accept: application/json, text/plain, */*\\r\\n' +\n        'Content-Type: application/json\\r\\n' +\n        'User-Agent: openclaw-lark/2026.4.1/mac\\r\\n' +\n        'Content-Length: 20\\r\\n' +\n        'Accept-Encoding: gzip, compress, deflate, br\\r\\n' +\n        'Host: open.feishu.cn\\r\\n' +\n        'Connection: keep-alive\\r\\n' +\n        '\\r\\n',\n```\nMissing the `Authorization: Bearer <tenant_access_token>` header.\nIf the token is NOT sent, does it return 400 or 401 or 404?\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_507460ede6c2bbcd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -i -X POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v1/openclaw_bot/ping -d '{\"needBotInfo\":true}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":3080,"output":393,"cacheRead":85177,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775565346399,"responseId":"chatcmpl-afb36a67-8bcf-4ae1-a178-63cc39e0dad3"}}
